milestones.description: Aarif Sheikh and Rohit Paudel's 104-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 100 between Aarif Sheikh and Rohit Paudel
Rohit Paudel has become the top scorer for NEP in ODIs with 588 runs, going past Malla's 480
Rohit Paudel's 126 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for NEP), surpassing Paras Khadka's 115
Rohit Paudel has broken the record for most sixes (10) in ODIs for NEP, going past Karan KC's 9
This is the highest match aggregate (578) involving teams P.N.G. & Nepal in ODIs
P.N.G.'s 6-run win against Nepal is the smallest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 14-run win against Hong Kong
Aarif Sheikh and Rohit Paudel's 104-run partnership is NEP's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 100 between Rohit Paudel and Aarif Sheikh
Sompal Kami has conceded the most runs in an innings (81) in ODIs for NEP, going past Lamichhane's record of 65
Rohit Paudel has scored 5 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for NEP breaking Malla's record
